content:
前端打完包之后用 Nginx 当反向代理，下面是从 0 上线的步骤。

## 0. /etc/nginx/nginx.conf 总开关

```nginx
user www-data;
worker_processes auto;
events { worker_connections 1024; }

http {
  sendfile on;
  keepalive_timeout 65;
  ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;
  gzip on;
  gzip_types text/plain text/css application/json application/javascript;
  access_log /var/log/nginx/access.log;
  error_log  /var/log/nginx/error.log;
  include /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/*;
}
```

## 1. 部署前端 dist

```bash
cp -r ~/repo/frontend/dist /var/www/labnotes
```

## 2. 站点配置 /etc/nginx/sites-available/labnotes

```nginx
server {
  listen 80;
  server_name labnotes.example.com;

  root /var/www/labnotes;
  index index.html;

  location / {
    try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;     # SPA fallback
  }

  location /api/ {
    proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8000/;
    proxy_set_header Host $host;
    proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
  }

  location ~* \.html$ {
    add_header Cache-Control "no-store";  # 强制刷新 index.html
  }

  location ~* \.(js|css|png|jpg|svg|woff2)$ {
    expires 30d;
    add_header Cache-Control "public, immutable";
  }
}
```

## 3. 启用 + 重启

```bash
sudo ln -sf /etc/nginx/sites-available/labnotes /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/
sudo nginx -t
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

`reload` 而不是 `restart` —— reload 复用现有连接，新配置生效不掉线。
